iv style=\"text-align: center; width: 100%\" class=\"imagecontainer\">\r\n<table style=\"text-align: center; width:100%;\">\r\n    <tbody>\r\n        <tr style=\"width:100%;\">\r\n            <td style=\"width:100%; text-align: center;\" align=\"center\"><img style=\"border: none\" alt=\"Nh\u1eadn \u0111\u1ecbnh U23 H\u1ed3ng K\u00f4ng vs U23 Palestine 16h00 ng\u00e0y 178 ASIAD h\u00ecnh \u1ea3nh\" title=\"Nh\u1eadn \u0111\u1ecbnh U23 H\u1ed3ng K\u00f4ng vs U23 Palestine 16h00 ng\u00e0y 178 ASIAD h\u00ecnh \u1ea3nh\" src=\"https://static.bongda24h.vn/medias/mobile/2018/8/17/u23hongkong.JPG\"></td>\r\n        </tr>\r\n        <tr>\r\n            <td style=\"text-align: center\">U23 H\u1ed3ng K\u00f4ng vs U23 Palestine</td>\r\n        </tr>\r\n    </tbody>\r\n</table>\r\n</div>\r\n<div style=\"text-align: left;\">\r\n<h2 style=\"color: rgb(0, 0, 0); font-family: Arial, Verdana, sans-serif; font-style: normal; font-variant-ligatures: normal; font-variant-caps: normal; letter-spacing: normal; orphans: 2; text-align: start; text-indent: 0px; text-transform: none; white-space: normal; widows: 2; word-spacing: 0px; -webkit-text-stroke-width: 0px; background-color: rgb(255, 255, 255); text-decoration-style: initial; text-decoration-color: initial;\"><span href=\"https://bongda24h.vn/nhan-dinh-bong-da-c344-p1.html\" target=\"_blank\">Nh\u1eadn \u0111\u1ecbnh b\u00f3ng \u0111\u00e1</span><span><span><span><span><span><span><span><span><span><span><span><span><span><span><span><span><span><span><span><span><span><span><span><span><span><span><span><span><span><span><span><span><span><span><span><span><span><span><span><span><span><span><span><span><span><span><span><span><span><span><span><span><span><span><span><span><span><span> </span></span>U23 H\u1ed3ng K\u00f4ng vs U23 Palestine: 1-3<br>\r\n</span></span></span></span></span></span></span></span></span></span></span></span></span></span></span></span></span></span></span></span></span></span></span></span></span></span></span></span></span></span></span></span></span></span></span></span></span></span></span></span></span></span></span></span></span></span></span></span></span></span></span></span></span></span></span></span></h2>\r\nU23 Palestine kh\u00f4ng \u0111\u01b0\u1ee3c \u0111\u00e1nh gi\u00e1 cao \u1edf m\u00f4n b\u00f3ng \u0111\u00e1 nam ASIAD 2018. Qu\u1ea3 th\u1ef1c \u0111\u1ed9i b\u00f3ng T\u00e2y \u00c1 c\u00f2n c\u00f3 s\u1ef1 kh\u1edfi \u0111\u1ea7u m\u1edd nh\u1ea1t khi \u0111\u1ec3 U23 \u0110\u00e0i Loan c\u1ea7m h\u00f2a kh\u00f4ng b\u00e0n th\u1eafng.<br>\r\n<br>\r\nTuy nhi\u00ean, \u0111o\u00e0n qu\u00e2n HLV Ayman Sandouqa c\u00e0ng ch\u01a1i c\u00e0ng hay. H\u1ecd th\u1eafng ng\u01b0\u1ee3c d\u00f2ng U23 L\u00e0o 2-1. L\u01b0\u1ee3t tr\u1eadn th\u1ee9 3, U23 Palestine ph\u1ea3i ch\u1ea1m tr\u00e1n \u0111\u1ed9i ch\u1ee7 nh\u00e0 Indonesia v\u00e0 h\u1ecd b\u1ea5t ng\u1edd gi\u00e0nh chi\u1ebfn th\u1eafng \u0111\u1ec3 t\u1ea1m v\u01b0\u01a1n l\u00ean ng\u00f4i \u0111\u1ea7u b\u1ea3ng A. Ch\u1ec9 c\u1ea7n m\u1ed9t chi\u1ebfn th\u1eafng n\u1eefa, U23 Palestine s\u1ebd ti\u1ebfn th\u1eb3ng v\u00e0o v\u00f2ng 1/8.<br>\r\n<br>\r\nTuy nhi\u00ean l\u01b0\u1ee3t tr\u1eadn cu\u1ed1i c\u00f9ng n\u00e0y, h\u1ecd s\u1ebd ph\u1ea3i \u0111\u1ed1i \u0111\u1ea7u U23 H\u1ed3ng K\u00f4ng c\u0169ng \u0111ang ch\u01a1i r\u1ea5t hay \u1edf ASIAD n\u0103m nay. \u0110\u1ed9i b\u00f3ng n\u00e0y m\u1edbi thi \u0111\u1ea5u 2 tr\u1eadn v\u00e0 th\u1eafng c\u1ea3 hai. U23 H\u1ed3ng K\u00f4ng c\u0169ng r\u1ea5t mu\u1ed1n th\u1eafng tr\u1eadn n\u00e0y \u0111\u1ec3 chi\u1ebfm ng\u00f4i \u0111\u1ea7u c\u00f9ng t\u1ea5m v\u00e9 \u0111i ti\u1ebfp. <br>\r\n<br>\r\nC\u1ea7n nh\u1edb U23 H\u1ed3ng K\u00f4ng \u0111\u00e3 \u0111\u00e8 b\u1eb9p U23 \u0110\u00e0i Loan t\u1eebng c\u1ea7m h\u00f2a Palestine t\u1edbi 4-0. \u0110\u00f3 c\u0169ng l\u00e0 l\u1eddi c\u1ea3nh b\u00e1o \u0111\u1ebfn \u0111\u1ed1i th\u1ee7 Palestine \u1edf cu\u1ed9c \u0111\u1ed1i \u0111\u1ea7u l\u1ea7n n\u00e0y.<br>\r\n<br>\r\nTuy nhi\u00ean, c\u00e1c chuy\u00ean gia v\u1eabn \u0111\u00e1nh gi\u00e1 U23 Palestine cao h\u01a1n. M\u1ed9t chi\u1ebfn th\u1eafng xem ra s\u1ebd thu\u1ed9c v\u1ec1 \u0111o\u00e0n qu\u00e2n HLV Ayman Sandouqa.<br>\r\n<br>\r\n\u0110\u1ed9i h\u00ecnh d\u1ef1 ki\u1ebfn c\u1ee7a 2 \u0111\u1ed9i:<br>\r\nU23 H\u1ed3ng K\u00f4ng (4-3-3): Ho Chun Yuen; Recio Comi, Wang Kit Tsui, Hok Ming Lau, Lilley Nunez; Remo Dujardin, Chun Lok Tan, Lam Ka Wai; Ching Lung Cheng, Wai Keung Chung, Siu Wai Chiu.<br>\r\nU23 Palestine: (4-4-2): Hamada Rami, Qatmish Ahmed, Rashid Mohamed, Termanini Michelmilad, Albahdari Abdallatif (C), Abuwarda Mahmoud, Dabbagh Oday, Yousef Mahmoud, Farawi Mousa, Maraaba Sameh, Darwish Mohamed.\r\n<div style=\"text-align: center; width: 100%\" class=\"imagecontainer\">\r\n<table style=\"text-align: center; width:100%;\">\r\n    <tbody>\r\n        <tr style=\"width:100%;\">\r\n            <td style=\"width:100%; text-align: center;\" align=\"center\"><img style=\"border: none\" alt=\"Xep hang hien tai o bang A Asiad 2018\" title=\"X\u1ebfp h\u1ea1ng hi\u1ec7n t\u1ea1i \u1edf b\u1ea3ng A Asiad 2018\" src=\"https://static.bongda24h.vn/medias/mobile/2018/8/17/bang-A.jpg\"></td>\r\n        </tr>\r\n        <tr>\r\n            <td style=\"text-align: center\">X\u1ebfp h\u1ea1ng hi\u1ec7n t\u1ea1i \u1edf b\u1ea3ng A Asiad 2018</td>\r\n        </tr>\r\n    </tbody>\r\n</table>\r\n</div>\r\n</div>\r\n<br></div><advbottom>","new_url":"","id":"2441","checkdouble":"194641"},{"date":"06:38 17/08","title":"Nh\u1eadn \u0111\u1ecbnh U23 Indonesia vs U23 L\u00e0o 19h ng\u00e0y 17/8 (ASIAD 2018)","type":"B\u00f3ng \u0111\u00e1 Anh","img_url":"https://static.bongda24h.vn/medias/thumnail/2018/8/17/nhan-dinh-u23-indonesia-vs-u23-lao-19h-ngay-178-asiad-2018.jpg","new_desc":"<link href='https://bongda24h.vn/websites/css/stylemobilev3.css?v=3' rel='stylesheet' type='text/css' /><style>body{margin:0px; padding:3px; font-size: 20px;}*{font-size:20px !important;}.articlerelatepannel { display:none; padding: 6px;  margin-top:5px; margin-bottom:5px; background-color:#f7f7f7; border:solid 1px #0cac0c}.mediaplayercontent{display:none;}h1{font-size:24px; font-weight:bold; color:black;}h2{font-weight:bold; color:black; width:100%; margin-top:5px !important;}h3{font-weight:bold; color:black;}iframe{display:none;}</style><div class='chitiet_tin'><h2>U23 Indonesia vs U23 L\u00e0o l\u00fac 19h ng\u00e0y 17/8 (V\u00f2ng b\u1ea3ng m\u00f4n b\u00f3ng \u0111\u00e1 nam Asian 2018): Nh\u1eadn \u0111\u1ecbnh b\u00f3ng \u0111\u00e1, \u00fd ki\u1ebfn chuy\u00ean gia, d\u1ef1 \u0111o\u00e1n k\u1ebft qu\u1ea3, ph\u00e2n t\u00edch chuy\u00ean m\u00f4n, c\u00e1c th\u00f4ng tin, th\u1ed1ng k\u00ea b\u00ean l\u1ec1 tr\u01b0\u1edbc tr\u1eadn \u0111\u1ea5u.</h2><div style=\"text-align: center; width: 100%\" class=\"imagecontainer\">\r\n<table style=\"text-align: center; width:100%;\">\r\n    <tbody>\r\n        <tr style=\"width:100%;\">\r\n            <td style=\"width:100%; text-align: center;\" align=\"center\"><img style=\"border: none\" alt=\"Nh\u1eadn \u0111\u1ecbnh U23 Indonesia vs U23 L\u00e0o 19h ng\u00e0y 178 ASIAD 2018 h\u00ecnh \u1ea3nh\" title=\"Nh\u1eadn \u0111\u1ecbnh U23 Indonesia vs U23 L\u00e0o 19h ng\u00e0y 178 ASIAD 2018 h\u00ecnh \u1ea3nh\" src=\"https://static.bongda24h.vn/medias/mobile/2018/8/17/u23-indonesia-vs-u23-lao.jpg\"></td>\r\n        </tr>\r\n        <tr>\r\n            <td style=\"text-align: center\">U23 Indonesia vs U23 L\u00e0o</td>\r\n        </tr>\r\n    </tbody>\r\n</table>\r\n</div>\r\n<br>\r\n<h2 style=\"color: rgb(0, 0, 0); font-family: Arial, Verdana, sans-serif; font-style: normal; font-variant-ligatures: normal; font-variant-caps: normal; letter-spacing: normal; text-indent: 0px; text-transform: none; white-space: normal; word-spacing: 0px; -webkit-text-stroke-width: 0px; background-color: rgb(255, 255, 255); text-decoration-style: initial; text-decoration-color: initial;\"><span href=\"https://bongda24h.vn/nhan-dinh-bong-da-c344-p1.html\" target=\"_blank\">Nh\u1eadn \u0111\u1ecbnh b\u00f3ng \u0111\u00e1</span><span><span><span><span><span><span><span><span><span><span><span><span><span><span><span><span><span><span><span><span><span><span><span><span><span><span><span><span><span><span><span><span><span><span><span><span><span><span><span><span><span><span><span><span><span><span><span><span><span><span><span><span><span><span><span><span><span><span> </span></span>U23 Indonesia vs U23 L\u00e0o: 5-1<br>\r\n</span></span></span></span></span></span></span></span></span></span></span></span></span></span></span></span></span></span></span></span></span></span></span></span></span></span></span></span></span></span></span></span></span></span></span></span></span></span></span></span></span></span></span></span></span></span></span></span></span></span></span></span></span></span></span></span></h2>\r\n<div>Th\u1ea5t b\u1ea1i tr\u01b0\u1edbc U23 Palestine khi\u1ebfn ch\u1ee7 nh\u00e0 Indonesia r\u01a1i v\u00e0o th\u1ebf kh\u00f3 \u1edf b\u1ea3ng A m\u00f4n b\u00f3ng \u0111\u00e1 nam Asiad 2018. Gi\u1edd \u0111\u00e2y, h\u1ecd bu\u1ed9c ph\u1ea3i th\u1eafng L\u00e0o chi\u1ec1u nay v\u00e0 h\u1ea1 g\u1ee5c \u0111\u1ed1i th\u1ee7 c\u1ea1nh tranh tr\u1ef1c ti\u1ebfp l\u00e0 H\u1ed3ng K\u00f4ng \u1edf tr\u1eadn \u0111\u1ea5u cu\u1ed1i (20/8) th\u00ec m\u1edbi c\u00f3 th\u1ec3 ch\u1eafc su\u1ea5t \u0111i ti\u1ebfp.\u00a0Tr\u01b0\u1edbc m\u1eaft, tr\u1eadn \u0111\u1ea5u v\u1edbi L\u00e0o kh\u00e1 \u0111\u01a1n gi\u1ea3n v\u00ec \u0111\u1ed1i th\u1ee7 n\u00e0y g\u1ea7n nh\u01b0 ch\u1eafc ch\u1eafn b\u1ecb lo\u1ea1i. <br>\r\n<br>\r\nTuy nhi\u00ean U23 L\u00e0o s\u1ebd c\u00f3 \u0111\u01b0\u1ee3c tinh th\u1ea7n tho\u1ea3i m\u00e1i song so s\u00e1nh v\u1ec1 m\u1ecdi m\u1eb7t th\u00ec \u0111\u1ea1i di\u1ec7n x\u1ee9 Tri\u1ec7u Voi kh\u00f4ng c\u00f3 c\u1eeda t\u1ea1o ra b\u1ea5t ng\u1edd nh\u1ea5t l\u00e0 khi U23 Indonesia quy\u1ebft th\u1eafng. U23 L\u00e0o ch\u1ec9 th\u01b0\u1eddng ch\u01a1i t\u1ed1t trong hi\u1ec7p 1. Sang hi\u1ec7p 2, h\u1ecd hay b\u1ecb xu\u1ed1ng s\u1ee9c d\u1eabn \u0111\u1ebfn ph\u1ea3i nh\u1eadn c\u00e1c b\u00e0n thua l\u00e3ng x\u1eb9t.<br>\r\n<br>\r\nU23 Indonesia c\u00f3 trong \u0111\u1ed9i h\u00ecnh nh\u1eefng c\u1ea7u th\u1ee7 kinh nghi\u1ec7m v\u00e0 bi\u1ebft khai th\u00e1c hi\u1ec7u qu\u1ea3 sai l\u1ea7m c\u1ee7a \u0111\u1ed1i th\u1ee7. Th\u00eam m\u1ed9t chi ti\u1ebft: Indonesia lu\u00f4n \u0111\u00e1 c\u1ef1c hay v\u00e0 th\u01b0\u1eddng th\u1eafng theo ki\u1ec3u h\u1ee7y di\u1ec7t m\u1ed7i khi g\u1eb7p c\u00e1c \u0111\u1ed1i th\u1ee7 d\u01b0\u1edbi c\u01a1.\r\n<div style=\"text-align: center; width: 100%\" class=\"imagecontainer\">\r\n<table style=\"text-align: center; width:100%;\">\r\n    <tbody>\r\n        <tr style=\"width:100%;\">\r\n            <td style=\"width:100%; text-align: center;\" align=\"center\"><img style=\"border: none\" alt=\"Xep hang hien tai o bang A Asiad 2018\" title=\"X\u1ebfp h\u1ea1ng hi\u1ec7n t\u1ea1i \u1edf b\u1ea3ng A Asiad 2018\" src=\"https://static.bongda24h.vn/medias/mobile/2018/8/17/bang-A.jpg\"></td>\r\n        </tr>\r\n        <tr>\r\n            <td style=\"text-align: center\">X\u1ebfp h\u1ea1ng hi\u1ec7n t\u1ea1i \u1edf b\u1ea3ng A Asiad 2018</td>\r\n        </tr>\r\n    </tbody>\r\n</table>\r\n</div>\r\n</div>\r\n<br></div><advbottom>","new_url":"","id":"2440","checkdouble":"194642"},{"date":"06:51 17/08","title":"Si\u00eau sao Ronaldo ch\u01b0a th\u1ec3 ra m\u1eaft Serie A v\u00e0o cu\u1ed1i tu\u1ea7n n\u00e0y?","type":"B\u00f3ng \u0111\u00e1 Anh","img_url":"https://static.bongda24h.vn/medias/original/2018/8/16/sieu-sao-ronaldo-chua-the-ra-mat-serie-a-vao-cuoi-tuan-nay.JPG","new_desc":"<link href='https://bongda24h.vn/websites/css/stylemobilev3.css?v=3' rel='stylesheet' type='text/css' /><style>body{margin:0px; padding:3px; font-size: 20px;}*{font-size:20px !important;}.articlerelatepannel { display:none; padding: 6px;  margin-top:5px; margin-bottom:5px; background-color:#f7f7f7; border:solid 1px #0cac0c}.mediaplayercontent{display:none;}h1{font-size:24px; font-weight:bold; color:black;}h2{font-weight:bold; color:black; width:100%; margin-top:5px !important;}h3{font-weight:bold; color:black;}iframe{display:none;}</style><div class='chitiet_tin'><h2>Nhi\u1ec1u \u0111\u1ed9i b\u00f3ng \u1edf Serie A \u0111\u1ed3ng lo\u1ea1t \u0111\u1ec1 xu\u1ea5t l\u00f9i l\u1ecbch thi \u0111\u1ea5u v\u00ec th\u1ea3m k\u1ecbch s\u1eadp c\u1ea7u Genoa h\u00f4m th\u1ee9 Ba v\u1eeba qua.</h2><div style=\"text-align: left;\">Theo l\u1ecbch, cu\u1ed1i tu\u1ea7n n\u00e0y Serie A 2018/19 s\u1ebd ch\u00ednh th\u1ee9c kh\u1edfi tranh v\u00e0 ng\u01b0\u1eddi ta \u0111ang ch\u1edd \u0111\u1ee3i tr\u1eadn \u0111\u1ea5u ra m\u1eaft ch\u00ednh th\u1ee9c c\u1ee7a Ronaldo trong m\u00e0u \u00e1o Juventus va c\u0169ng l\u00e0 tr\u1eadn \u0111\u1ea7u ti\u00ean c\u1ee7a anh trong s\u1ef1 nghi\u1ec7p t\u1ea1i \u0111\u1ea5u tr\u01b0\u1eddng c\u1ea5p CLB s\u1ed1 1 Italia. Tuy nhi\u00ean, \u0111i\u1ec1u n\u00e0y c\u00f3 th\u1ec3 b\u1ecb tr\u00ec ho\u00e3n do th\u1ea3m k\u1ecbch s\u1eadp c\u1ea7u h\u00f4m th\u1ee9 Ba v\u1eeba qua.\r\n<div style=\"text-align: center; width: 100%\" class=\"imagecontainer\">\r\n<table style=\"text-align: center; width:100%;\">\r\n    <tbody>\r\n        <tr style=\"width:100%;\">\r\n            <td style=\"width:100%; text-align: center;\" align=\"center\"><img style=\"border: none\" alt=\"Si\u00eau sao Ronaldo ch\u01b0a th\u1ec3 ra m\u1eaft, v\u00f2ng 1 Serie A 201819 b\u1ecb ho\u00e3n h\u00ecnh \u1ea3nh\" title=\"Si\u00eau sao Ronaldo ch\u01b0a th\u1ec3 ra m\u1eaft, v\u00f2ng 1 Serie A 201819 b\u1ecb ho\u00e3n h\u00ecnh \u1ea3nh\" src=\"https://static.bongda24h.vn/medias/mobile/2018/8/16/sieu-sao-ronaldo-lai-ghi-ban-trong-mau-ao-juventus.JPG\"></td>\r\n        </tr>\r\n        <tr>\r\n            <td style=\"text-align: center\">\u00a0</td>\r\n        </tr>\r\n    </tbody>\r\n</table>\r\n</div>\r\n<br>\r\n<br>\r\nV\u1ee5 s\u1ee5p \u0111\u1ed5 c\u00e2y c\u1ea7u cao t\u1ed1c \u1edf Genoa \u0111\u00e3 khi\u1ebfn 39 ng\u01b0\u1eddi thi\u1ec7t m\u1ea1ng. Hi\u1ec7n c\u00e1c c\u01a1 quan ch\u1ee9c n\u0103ng \u0111\u1ecba ph\u01b0\u01a1ng v\u1eabn \u0111ang t\u00ecm ki\u1ebfm c\u00e1c n\u1ea1n nh\u00e2n c\u00f2n s\u1ed1ng s\u00f3t.<br>\r\n<br>\r\nTr\u01b0\u1edbc th\u1ea3m k\u1ecbch n\u00e0y, 1 s\u1ed1 \u0111\u1ed9i b\u00f3ng \u1edf Serie A \u0111\u00e3 \u0111\u1ec1 xu\u1ea5t BTC gi\u1ea3i l\u00f9i l\u1ecbch thi \u0111\u1ea5u. Tr\u01b0\u1edbc m\u1eaft, 2 tr\u1eadn \u0111\u1ea5u gi\u1eefa Sampdoria - Fiorentina v\u00e0 Milan - Genoa \u0111\u00e3 \u0111\u01b0\u1ee3c BTC \u0111\u1ed3ng \u00fd ho\u00e3n l\u1ea1i.<br>\r\n<br>\r\nPh\u00eda Juventus ch\u01b0a \u0111\u01b0a ra b\u1ea5t k\u1ef3 th\u00f4ng b\u00e1o n\u00e0o nh\u01b0ng ch\u1ee7 t\u1ecbch c\u1ee7a Sampdoria \u0111\u00e3 l\u00ean ti\u1ebfng x\u00e1c nh\u1eadn Bianconeri c\u0169ng s\u1ebd kh\u00f4ng thi \u0111\u1ea5u v\u00e0o th\u1ee9 B\u1ea3y. Ch\u1ee7 t\u1ecbch Sampdoria, Massimo Ferrero ti\u1ebft l\u1ed9: \"T\u00f4i \u0111\u00e3 n\u00f3i chuy\u1ec7n v\u1edbi Agnelli, \u00f4ng \u1ea5y n\u00f3i v\u1edbi t\u00f4i r\u1eb1ng Juve s\u1ebd kh\u00f4ng thi \u0111\u1ea5u. Kh\u00f4ng th\u1ec3 ngh\u0129 \u0111\u1ebfn vi\u1ec7c \u0111\u00e1 b\u00f3ng \u1edf th\u1eddi \u0111i\u1ec3m n\u00e0y. Th\u1ee9 B\u1ea3y s\u1ebd di\u1ec5n ra qu\u1ed1c tang\".<br>\r\n<br>\r\nTrong khi \u0111\u00f3, 1 tuy\u00ean b\u1ed1 t\u1eeb Fiorentina cho bi\u1ebft: \"L\u00fac n\u00e0y \u0111\u00e1ng \u0111\u1ec3 b\u00f3ng \u0111\u00e1 \u00dd d\u1eebng l\u1ea1i, th\u01b0\u01a1ng ti\u1ebfc v\u00e0 t\u00f4n tr\u1ecdng tang l\u1ec5 c\u1ee7a h\u00e0ng ch\u1ee5c gia \u0111\u00ecnh. B\u00f3ng \u0111\u00e1 l\u00e0 \u0111am m\u00ea v\u00e0 ni\u1ec1m vui nh\u01b0ng \u0111\u00e2y l\u00e0 kho\u1ea3nh kh\u1eafc \u0111au \u0111\u1edbn. T\u1ea5t c\u1ea3 ch\u00fang ta ph\u1ea3i \u1edf b\u00ean c\u1ea1nh Genoa\".<br>\r\n<br>\r\nCh\u01b0a c\u00f3 th\u00f4ng b\u00e1o ch\u00ednh th\u1ee9c t\u1eeb Juventus v\u00e0 BTC Serie A nh\u01b0ng nhi\u1ec1u kh\u1ea3 n\u0103ng tr\u1eadn \u0111\u1ea5u gi\u1eefa L\u00e3o b\u00e0 v\u00e0 Chievo v\u00e0o \u0111\u00eam th\u1ee9 B\u1ea3y s\u1ebd b\u1ecb ho\u00e3n l\u1ea1i. \u0110i\u1ec1u \u0111\u00f3 \u0111\u1ed3ng ngh\u0129a, NHM s\u1ebd ph\u1ea3i ch\u1edd th\u00eam th\u1eddi gian \u0111\u1ec3 \u0111\u01b0\u1ee3c ch\u1ee9ng ki\u1ebfn nh\u1eefng b\u01b0\u1edbc ch\u1ea1y \u0111\u1ea7u ti\u00ean c\u1ee7a Ronaldo \u1edf Serie A.</div></div><advbottom>","new_url":"","id":"2439","checkdouble":"194644"}]}